                                                                                              AC-03(08)       ACCESS ENFORCEMENT | REVOCATION OF ACCESS AUTHORIZATIONS
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              AC-03(08)_ODP         rules governing the ming of revocaons of access authorizaons are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              AC-03(08)[01]         revocaon of access authorizaons is enforced, resulng from changes to the
                                                                                                                                    security aributes of subjects based on <AC-03(08)_ODP rules>;

                                                                                                              AC-03(08)[02]         revocaon of access authorizaons is enforced resulng from changes to the
                                                                                                                                    security aributes of objects based on <AC-03(08)_ODP rules>.

